    "body": "This is a very recent addition so we should be a bit careful in case it gets backed out. But from Python 3.15b1 we should be able use use PyObject_CallFinalizerFromDealloc in the Limited API.",
    "closed_at": null,
    "comment_data": [
        {
            "_links": {
