                    "href": "https://api.github.com/repos/cython/cython/pulls/comments/3182171323"
                }
            },
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "I don't normally try to gate Limited API versions with alphas (because you need to check `PY_VERSION_HEX` separately. But given it's very new it's probably worth it for now.",
            "commit_id": "5e211a634eee9d03e4613164eefae8d47f48e9c6",
            "created_at": "2026-05-04T14:16:24Z",
            "diff_hunk": "@@ -262,7 +262,7 @@\n   #define CYTHON_USE_SYS_MONITORING 0\n   #ifndef CYTHON_USE_TP_FINALIZE\n     // PyObject_CallFinalizerFromDealloc is missing and not easily replaced\n-    #define CYTHON_USE_TP_FINALIZE 0\n+    #define CYTHON_USE_TP_FINALIZE (__PYX_LIMITED_VERSION_HEX >= 0x030F0000 && PY_VERSION_HEX > 0x030F00A8)",
